Veterinary Hospital Management:
================================

To use this application you may need to have

Ruby Version >= 2
Rails Version >= 4

Clone this repository to your local machine and switch to project path
Run the following commands

$bundle install

Note: I have used Mysql as my database, you may use postgres or any rdbms that rails supports by adding relevan gem to Gemfile 

Database Setup:
---------------
Configure database.yml with adapter specific credentials


$rake db:create
$rake db:migrate
$rake db:seed

It creates 5 sample users with 4 different roles

Start Rails Server
$rails s

Goto browser and type http://localhost:3000 and login with admin user

email    : admin@gmail.com
password : admin123

